      • WeaponData

        public WeaponData​(Weapon weapon)
        Instantiates a new Weapon data. Every weapon can have one or two primary effect, one secondary and one tertiary. Gets weapon cost to buy the weapon or the recharge cost. Controls if the weapon's loaded.
        Parameters:
        weapon - the weapon
